SHOW DETAILS:

Japanizi: Going, Going, Gong!
Contestants compete with a teammate against other teams as they tackle obstacles and challenges to test their mental capabilities, strength, endurance, and smarts.

Japanizi is an adaptation of the ABC reality show I Survived A Japanese Game Show. The studio-based kids game show will make use of zany costumes, conveyor belts, dizzy chairs, giant fans and velcro walls with themed competitions and more. The Japanese language is incorporated with the show, but it is mostly English.
